Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's his real body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.17,0:00:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,After twenty years,\Nwhat say we face each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.43,0:00:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I flew back as quickly\Nas I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,More to the point,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you took too long to send over\Na substitute border guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your planning was bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no way to show\Nyour appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I carried out your selfish request\Ndespite recovering from an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.20,0:01:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... Shall we get going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.93,0:01:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It can still move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.70,0:02:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I'd expect\Nfrom my old granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder this little girl was able\Nto dodge my hidden weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the old lady who can see\Npast my attacks was controlling
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the little girl with Chakra threads\Nused for the Puppet Master Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, you were so kind as to\Nattach threads of Chakra to Hiruko's tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But to think that I'd notice it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,after the tail's motion had been\Nbrought to a halt...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was when you first attacked\Nwith the Kunai Knife, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Threads of Chakra attached\Nto the Kunai Knife
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,latched onto the tail\Nwhen it repelled the Kunai Knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppressed my Chakra as much\Nas possible so as not to be seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet you still figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm amazed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the one who hammered\Nthe principles of puppetry into me was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,none other than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But the show ends today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my intention as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, will things proceed\Nas simply as that, I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Chiyo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Chiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he... Is he Sasori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's just as he was before...\N{\i1}He hasn't aged a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was told Sasori broke off from\N{\i1}the Hidden Sand 20 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way that\N{\i1}he could be this young.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:10.47,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(690,587)}Sasori's Real Face\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The sound that I heard coming\N{\i1}from inside just a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no doubt that\N{\i1}the battle has already begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd like to get a grasp\N{\i1}of the situation, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Return Gaara to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's only a matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}before my man Sasori does away\N{\i1}with the group inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If my man comes out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then the whole point of using this one\N{\i1}to draw out the Jinchuriki will be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk!\NI won't let you get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei,\Nyou go look after Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Guy, how are conditions\Nover there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry Kakashi, it looks like things\Nwill still take a while over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.05,0:07:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If detaining someone is your objective,\Nthere's no better way than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If your opponent has exactly\Nthe same abilities as you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably won't be that easy\Nto bring matters to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Splendid move, Mr. Imposter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... Looks like it's impossible to\Nexpect back-up for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura, Granny Chiyo,\N{\i1}hold down the fort a bit longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I'm going\Nto let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Better keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And then,\NI will settle matters properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.44,0:09:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Kankuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What do you think\Nyou're doing, Kankuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to rest easy\Nin a situation like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so impatient...\NThat's not like you, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Miss Temari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little while...\NIf we rest just a little while,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be able to start\Nrunning again right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let us rest a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys have no discipline.\NAnd you call yourselves Shinobi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.85,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys took turns guarding\Nthe border for a whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And no sooner had they returned\Nto the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,they had to run all the way here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,However top-notch Shinobi they may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't force them to do\Nmore than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be resting while\NLord Gaara is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We should do what we can\Nfor the Kazekage's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.71,0:10:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, for the Kazekage's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Temari! Let's head out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys! That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now,\Nyou shouldn't get so fired up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebizo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A Shinobi should never lose\Nhis composure under any circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgetting that and pursuing\Nthe enemy too far all by himself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,was the cause of\NKankuro's recent failure, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, in your current state,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,all of you are not being aware\Nof your surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the remains of the battle\Nthat Akatsuki fought with the Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. You have to assume that\Nwe have already entered their territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what kind of traps\Nthey may have set up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're about to set foot\Nin such a place,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be annihilated in no time\Nif you go dashing in,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.01,0:11:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,exhausted the way you all are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,While you're resting, I'll tell you all\Na story about the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was long, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you must\Nhave heard of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The incident of the Third Kazekage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third...Kazekage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... The one before\Nthe previous Kazekage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all the Kazekage\Ndown through history,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the Third Kazekage was\Nsaid to be the most powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the incident occurred when\Nsomeone kidnapped the Kazekage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire village got all excited\Nand went out seeking news
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,of what had become of\Nthe Third Kazekage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.64,0:12:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back upon it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you would have to say\Nthat they simply lost their cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The village's guard wore thin, allowing\N the enemy to intrude, and panic ensued.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If they had dealt with it\Na little more coolly at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the subsequent war\Ncould have been avoided.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I am painfully aware of how\Nyou all feel right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...you mustn't repeat\Nthe same mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.88,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that were made back in\Nthe days of the Third Kazekage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ebizo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,did they ever learn what happened to\Nthe Third Kazekage after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, the Anbu Black Ops\Ncontinued to investigate in secret,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but no body was ever found,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,nor any sign that the Kazekage\Nhad been removed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Granny Chiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you so filled with emotion\Nthat you cannot speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it's our first reunion\Nin 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.08,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasori, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,While I'm at it,\NI'll show you something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's guaranteed to move you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A collection that gave me\Na hard time when trying to kill it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I like this best of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That... It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.21,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...the Third Kazekage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Third...Kazekage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.83,0:15:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that take you back,\NGranny Chiyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.87,0:15:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Chiyo, the Third Kazekage...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this have happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It was over ten years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that the Third Kazekage suddenly\Ndisappeared from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We scoured the countryside,\Nbut we were never able to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the most powerful\Nof all the Kazekage's, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasori, you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And so what if I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.51,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean to say that a retired old lady\Nwith one foot in the grave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,is about to avenge\Nthe Third Kazekage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.21,0:15:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Retired, with one foot in the grave.\NThat may be so,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was worth hauling\Nmy heavy behind over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have too many regrets\Nif I were to die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's bad enough that my grandson
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,got himself mixed up\Nwith a bad crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but to think that you'd betray the village
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to meddle with the Kazekage,\Nfor the third time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Third time?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.52,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Orochimaru\Nwho killed Gaara's father,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the Fourth Kazekage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who guided them\Nwas Sasori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And this time,\NGaara and even the Third Kazekage...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, I don't know anything\Nabout the Fourth Kazekage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who guided them\Nwas my subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, it's the same\Nas if you did it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really say that\Nyou were not involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I was originally paired with\NOrochimaru back at the Akatsuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so I did lots of things but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were paired\Nwith Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,then that means you know\Nabout Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, there're a lot\Nof questions I need you to answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately,\NI must take you two out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and go capture that Jinchuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to keep people waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have no time\Nto answer your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,shall we get right to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To think that Hiruko's tail\N{\i1}fell to pieces...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some\Npretty good moves, Granny Chiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.23,0:18:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.16,0:18:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn. Did I botch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.28,0:19:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the old lady manipulating things,\N{\i1}it's impossible to get anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.21,0:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Sakura! Hold your breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it poison?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this poisonous smoke,\N{\i1}your movements will be irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
